About Gator Chevrolet
Why Choose Gator Chevrolet - Discover the Gator Difference:
At Gator Chevrolet, we're more than just a dealership; we're a family-owned and operated business nestled in the heart of North Central Florida. Our commitment is simple: to provide unparalleled customer service and offer the lowest prices on both
new
and
used
vehicles. Our focus is exclusively on you, our valued guest.From your very first interaction with us, we take a consultative approach, working together to pinpoint your unique needs and desires. Then, we match those preferences with the perfect vehicle that fulfills your wishes. Our extensive inventory boasts the most sought-after vehicles, complete with a variety of colors, options, and trim levels to meet today's discerning buyer's demands. Rest assured, our
pre-owned
vehicles are meticulously reconditioned to maintain peak reliability.But our service doesn't stop there. We pride ourselves on our ability to find car
financing
solutions that align with your budget and terms. We collaborate with over 25 local, regional, and national banks, all vying for the chance to earn your business.What truly sets Gator Chevrolet apart are the exceptional protection packages we offer through
Allstate® Vehicle Protection Products
. Allstate is a trusted and financially stable name across the United States. Our affordable protection plans provide years of confidence, peace of mind, and safeguard you against unexpected expenses that can arise from vehicle ownership.When you're in the market for a new or used vehicle, remember Gator Chevrolet – where your satisfaction is our top priority.
Locally owned and operated.
We will BEAT any local advertised price!
Get top dollar for your trade.
Get our best price in minutes!
We will buy your car for cash - even if you don't buy ours.
If we don't have the vehicle you want, let us know and we will find it.
We offer financing and work with local, regional and national banks to serve all your financing needs.
Open 6 days a week to better serve you.
Gator Chevrolet
208 Hatley Street E, Jasper, FL 32052
